---
/*
  Meet Your Chauffeur — founder section.
  ALL [FILL IN] items must be provided by Vitaly before launch.
  This section earns the premium price. Do not launch without it.
*/
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="py-20 sm:py-24 px-4 bg-charcoal-800"
  aria-labelledby="about-heading"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 lg:gap-20 items-center">

      <!-- Photo column -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!--
          PLACEHOLDER: Portrait photo of Vitaly.
          Shot direction: three-quarter shot, slightly turned toward camera.
          Setting: beside or in front of the S-Class, rear door open.
          Clothing: dark suit, white shirt, no tie OR subtle tie.
          Lighting: soft natural light or golden hour.
          Minimum: 1200×1600px, deliver as WebP + JPEG.
          The current /mychauffeur.jpg is used as a temporary placeholder only.
        -->
        <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-charcoal-700 relative">
          <img
            src="/mychauffeur.jpg"
            alt="Vitaly — founder and lead chauffeur of Vitaly Executive Chauffeur, Dublin"
            width="800"
            height="1000"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <!-- Gold accent line -->
          <div
            class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-24 h-24 border-r-2 border-b-2 border-gold-500/40 rounded-br-xl"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Years driving badge -->
        <div
          class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 sm:-top-5 sm:-left-5 bg-charcoal-900
                 border border-gold-500/30 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-xl shadow-black/50"
        >
          <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gold-400 leading-none">
            [FILL IN]<span class="text-lg">+</span>
          </p><!-- PLACEHOLDER: Number of years driving in Dublin -->
          <p class="text-xs text-white/50 mt-1 leading-tight">years driving<br />in Dublin</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Copy column -->
      <div>
        <span class="gold-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <p class="text-gold-400 text-xs tracking-[0.35em] uppercase mb-3">Your chauffeur</p>

        <h2 id="about-heading" class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
          <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Use Vitaly's actual first name throughout this section -->
          Meet [FILL IN: First name]
        </h2>

        <!--
          PLACEHOLDER: All bracketed facts must come from Vitaly.
          The structure below is a template — rewrite the sentences once you have the facts.
          What to provide:
            - Years driving in Dublin
            - Previous employer (hotel, corporate, private family, etc.)
            - Languages spoken
            - Any professional qualifications (PSV, IMTA membership, etc.)
            - One personal detail that builds trust (e.g. "grew up in Dublin 4",
              "former concierge at the Merrion Hotel", "speaks Russian and English")
        -->
        <div class="space-y-4 text-white/65 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          <p>
            [FILL IN: First name] has been driving Dublin's roads for
            [FILL IN: X] years. Before founding Vitaly Executive Chauffeur,
            [he/she] worked as [FILL IN: previous role — e.g. "senior chauffeur for
            a Dublin 4 family office"] for [FILL IN: X] years, where
            [FILL IN: one concrete thing learned — e.g. "punctuality and discretion
            weren't optional, they were the job"].
          </p>
          <p>
            [FILL IN: First name] speaks [FILL IN: languages, e.g. "English and Russian"]
            and holds a full PSV licence (no. [FILL IN: PSV number]).
            [FILL IN: One more personal sentence — e.g. "He started this business
            because he wanted to give clients something the apps can't: a driver
            who knows your name and answers the phone."]
          </p>
          <p>
            Every car is prepared personally before each booking —
            valeted, fuelled, and stocked — so that when you get in,
            you can stop thinking about the journey and start thinking
            about where you're going.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Credential pills -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/70 bg-charcoal-900
                       border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
            Garda-vetted
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/70 bg-charcoal-900
                       border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z"/>
            </svg>
            PSV licensed
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/70 bg-charcoal-900
                       border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"/>
            </svg>
            [FILL IN: languages] spoken
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/70 bg-charcoal-900
                       border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            [FILL IN: X]+ years in Dublin
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <a
          href="/#booking"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-gold-500 hover:bg-gold-600
                 text-charcoal-900 font-semibold tracking-wide rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >
          Book with [FILL IN: First name]<!-- PLACEHOLDER: use first name -->
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
